---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="Richmond Hill 列治文山家庭法律师 | 何淼律师 | 离婚 · 子女监护 · 婚前协议"
    description="何淼律师（Miao He）为 Richmond Hill 列治文山华人提供中英双语家庭法服务。离婚、子女监护、婚前协议、跨境资产。647-930-6688。"
  />
  <meta name="keywords" content="Richmond Hill家庭法律师,列治文山离婚律师,Richmond Hill divorce lawyer,列治文山华人律师,Chinese family lawyer Richmond Hill,何淼律师" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Richmond Hill 列治文山家庭法律师 | 何淼律师" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="何淼律师为 Richmond Hill 提供中英双语家庭法服务。离婚、子女监护、婚前协议。647-930-6688。" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/richmond-hill-family-lawyer" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/richmond-hill-family-lawyer" />
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "LegalService",
    "name": "何淼律师 — Richmond Hill 家庭法律师",
    "url": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/richmond-hill-family-lawyer",
    "telephone": "+1-647-930-6688",
    "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Richmond Hill", "containedInPlace": { "@type": "Province", "name": "Ontario" }},
    "provider": { "@type": "Person", "name": "Miao He", "alternateName": "何淼" },
    "serviceType": ["Family Law", "Divorce", "Child Custody", "Prenuptial Agreement"],
    "inLanguage": ["zh", "en"]
  }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">首页</a> › <a href="/contact">服务地区</a> › Richmond Hill 列治文山</div>
        <h1>Richmond Hill 列治文山家庭法律师</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">何淼律师（Miao He）· 中英双语 · 紧邻列治文山 · 647-930-6688</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container content-grid">
        <div class="main-content">
          <div class="definition-box">
            <p>Richmond Hill（列治文山）与 Markham 毗邻，是 GTA 华人高度聚集的城市之一。何淼律师事务所位于 Markham，距列治文山仅数分钟车程，为当地华人家庭提供便捷的中英双语家庭法服务。</p>
          </div>
          <h2>Richmond Hill 华人家庭常见法律问题</h2>
          <p>列治文山华人社区的家庭法案件常涉及高价值房产分割、子女教育安排争议，以及国内资产转移等问题。何淼律师具备处理这类复杂案件的丰富经验。</p>
          <h3>离婚与财产分割</h3>
          <p>Ontario《家庭法》规定，婚姻期间净资产增值须在离婚时平均分配（Equalization）。房产、投资账户、养老金均在分割范围内。何淼律师协助客户准确计算净家庭财产（NFP），保护合法权益。</p>
          <h3>子女监护与抚养</h3>
          <p>列治文山华人家庭在子女监护争议中，常见双方对子女就读学校、是否回中国探亲等问题产生分歧。何淼律师协助制定详尽的育儿计划（Parenting Plan），减少日后争议。</p>
          <h3>婚前与婚后协议</h3>
          <p>列治文山豪宅区的家庭对婚前协议需求较高，尤其涉及父母首付款、家族信托资产保护。何淼律师提供全中文起草及法律意见。</p>
          <h3>紧急动议与资产保全</h3>
          <p>如怀疑配偶转移资产或带走子女，何淼律师可迅速申请临时禁止令（Restraining Order）或资产冻结令，保护客户权益。</p>
          <div class="qa-block">
            <h3>Q：列治文山的案件在哪个法院处理？</h3>
            <p>A：列治文山家庭法案件通常在 Newmarket 的 York Region Family Court 处理。何淼律师对该法院流程熟悉，可高效推进案件。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-box">
            <h3>预约 Richmond Hill 家庭法咨询</h3>
            <p>初次咨询 30 分钟，$220 + HST。中英双语，无需翻译。</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">立即预约</a>
            <a href="tel:6479306688" class="btn-secondary">647-930-6688</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>联系何淼律师</h3>
            <p>📞 <a href="tel:6479306688">647-930-6688</a></p>
            <p>📧 <a href="mailto:miao@miaohelaw.ca">miao@miaohelaw.ca</a></p>
            <p>📍 Markham（服务 Richmond Hill）</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>服务项目</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>离婚诉讼</li><li>子女监护</li><li>婚前协议</li>
              <li>财产分割</li><li>抚养费</li><li>跨境资产</li><li>分居协议</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>服务语言</h3>
            <p>🇨🇳 普通话（Mandarin）</p>
            <p>🇨🇦 英文（English）</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
<style>
  .page-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C1810 0%, #4A2C1A 100%); color: white; padding: 3rem 0 2rem; }
  .page-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #ffffff; }
  .hero-sub { color: #D4A853; margin: 0; }
  .breadcrumb { font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.7; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .breadcrumb a { color: white; text-decoration: none; }
  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .content-section { padding: 3rem 0; }
  .content-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px; gap: 3rem; }
  .definition-box { background: #FDF6EC; border-left: 4px solid #9A8060; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; }
  .qa-block { background: #f8f8f8; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .qa-block h3 { color: #2C1810; margin-top: 0; font-size: 1rem; }
  .cta-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C1810, #4A2C1A); color: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .cta-box h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #D4A853; }
  .btn-primary { display: inline-block; background: #D4A853; color: #2C1810; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; margin: 0.5rem; }
  .btn-secondary { display: inline-block; background: transparent; color: white; border: 2px solid white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; margin: 0.5rem; }
  .sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .sidebar-card { background: white; border: 1px solid #e8e0d5; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.2rem; }
  .sidebar-card h3 { color: #2C1810; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e0d5; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .sidebar-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .sidebar-card li { padding: 0.3rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ebe3; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .sidebar-card a { color: #9A8060; text-decoration: none; }
  h2 { color: #2C1810; margin-top: 2rem; }
  h3 { color: #4A2C1A; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .page-hero h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; } }
</style>
